{"tid":1740017,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2018年預言的香港未來國運","createTime":"2019-11-19T21:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T03:23:41.000Z","uid":119572,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2c7b75e9610dde1bf9ddccf5f35511ebe47f0832","tid":1740017,"uid":119572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:47:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.xuite.net/blog/bestdavid.lin/eching/585555180\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.xuite.net%2Fblog%2Fbestdavid.lin%2Feching%2F585555180&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNrhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=03caa15f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.xuite.net/blog/bestdavid.lin/eching/585555180</a><br />\n<br />\nA01-2019年。預言: 中國規畫30年之後要直接統治香港，就必須要能夠爆中國統治內幕，顯示中國內部行政單位都是非常遵守統治規則。假如沒有這個行動，暗示，2047一國兩制結束之後的香港統治，中國缺乏信心。<br />\n<br />\nA02-<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2018-2020預言:香港人民對自己的未來，將很長一段時間，陷入莽莽歧途，墜入五里霧中。三年之久(很久很久)都無法擺脫。</span></span>【2018港股大跌，2020年會是谷底了，但是，基本上，經濟繁榮基礎還是安全的。不會進入大蕭條或是房價崩潰到只剩20%的慘狀】<br />\n<br />\nA03- <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2019。2017年香港民主制度的某些關鍵功能會被廢棄。2019年經濟非常不景氣，才後悔廢棄那個機制。大約2020年之後，恢復那個民主機制，最終是吉。</span></span><br />\n(真普選？）<br />\n<br />\nA04-<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2019年，爆發香港人和中共的另一次衝突，香港政府會有巨大的受傷而損失形象。</span></span><br />\n（流血運動？）<br />\n<br />\nA05- 2018-19。<br />\n規劃讓香港融入中國，當中國財政金融皇冠上的明珠。精心規劃香港為高獲利金融中心。【只是規劃，不是執行喔 ! 】<br />\n<br />\nA06-黃之鋒。2019(23歲)。假如出現強勢獨裁姿態的時候，就顯示下一波，未來六年，他領導的革命不會成功。<br />\n<br />\nA07-黃之鋒。<br />\n2019。(姤卦)忽然出現政治發展的大好機會。<br />\n2019。(賁卦)成為某些資深機構的領袖之一。因此爭取到一些資深機構的支持。<br />\n<br />\nA08- 2029-2033，廣東和香港政治地位急速升起。<br />\n<br />\nA09-2019-2020中國建設得特別有遠景的新城鎮，不得不要轉給西方/香港/台灣特權財團去經營治理。(新租借形成)<br />\n<br />\n----"},{"pid":"7de8cc43bfc3321d1888a6cdc848f6e6d44f844f","tid":1740017,"uid":185416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:52:34.000Z","msg":"準.."},{"pid":"0d83e474c5230785d036a82324e711e9c2e55c24","tid":1740017,"uid":185416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:54:12.000Z","msg":"A09應該係貿易談判內容"},{"pid":"751a31555c8e8c4e8fcd48e6cf1da858cf157064","tid":1740017,"uid":290205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:54:37.000Z","msg":"五里霧...真係諷刺"},{"pid":"593df7f6b4087894bb1c13d6fe67d438db9336c1","tid":1740017,"uid":270872,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:58:15.000Z","msg":"會有新租借<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d077f8fa502c2eec70784f892d5c06f82f71782e","tid":1740017,"uid":119572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T22:04:04.000Z","msg":"希望俾到大家少少希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n堅持下去就有勝利"},{"pid":"96b7894eb1030e21c2844acaac285c1ddefb6a2a","tid":1740017,"uid":6142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T22:08:10.000Z","msg":"係真就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e272dd45a494ddcb446a9fadc0a4f186628afae","tid":1740017,"uid":56698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"751a31555c8e8c4e8fcd48e6cf1da858cf157064","tid":1740017,"uid":290205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:54:37.000Z","msg":"五里霧...真係諷刺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T22:44:02.000Z","msg":"可能一直嘅方法都係錯"},{"pid":"e707374691af6182e7503a8e7251a1e81122896b","tid":1740017,"uid":119572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:51:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74377fb4dca6b2b8f54b9c285eba8b200d363ad3","tid":1740017,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:00:10.000Z","msg":"中左頭幾個"},{"pid":"1e692ad5e75db3c982ef0544d5ddec4778eb2a0c","tid":1740017,"uid":92908